OL,3,CRape suspects' arrests delayed as
OL,4,Cpolice diverted to festivals, watchdog
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FPolice are delaying arresting rape
OL,8,Fsuspects and cancelling appointments
OL,9,Fwith victims because investigators are
OL,10,Fbeing sent to staff football matches
OL,11,Fand festivals, a watchdog has warned.
OL,13,FInspector of Constabulary Michelle
OL,14,FSkeer made a string of recommendations
OL,15,Fas she urged forces to make
OL,16,Fimprovements after also finding
OL,17,Fseveral of the officers in rape
OL,18,Finvestigation teams at forces visited
OL,19,Fby the watchdog were trainees who were
OL,20,Fnot fully qualified.
