OL,3,CRape suspects' arrests delayed as
OL,4,Cpolice diverted to festivals, watchdog
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FThe report from His Majesty's
OL,8,FInspectorate of Constabulary and Fire
OL,9,Fand Rescue Services (HMICFRS),
OL,10,Fpublished on Thursday, said: "In half
OL,11,Fthe forces we inspected, Rasso (rape
OL,12,Fand serious sexual offences) personnel
OL,13,Fare routinely diverted to supporting
OL,14,Fevents such as football matches and
OL,15,Ffestivals.
OL,17,F"Forces should recognise that this
OL,18,Fmeans Rasso investigators end up
OL,19,Fcancelling appointments with victims
OL,20,For delaying arrests. It only adds to
OL,21,Ftheir workload pressure."
