OL,4,Cpolice diverted to festivals, watchdog
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FAt the time, the College of Policing
OL,8,Fsaid 4,540 officers in England and
OL,9,FWales had completed specialist
OL,10,Ftraining on investigating rape and
OL,11,Fsexual offences.
OL,13,FThe College - the body responsible for
OL,14,Fpolice training - said officers had
OL,15,Fbeen trained in each of the 43 forces
OL,16,Facross the two nations but did not
OL,17,Fdisclose how many officers per force
OL,18,Fhave received the training.
