OL,7,FA Home Office spokesperson said: "This
OL,8,Fgovernment will make sure victims of
OL,9,Frape or sexual abuse get the justice
OL,10,Fthey deserve.
OL,12,F"While we welcome the progress being
OL,13,Fmade, in far too many cases victims
OL,14,Fare being let down. That's why it is
OL,15,Fso important that the police continue
OL,16,Fto make long-lasting improvements and
OL,17,Fput perpetrators behind bars.
